name: 2024 the 4th International Conference on Information Communication and Software Engineering
content: Publication: Submitted paper will be peer reviewed by conference committees, and accepted papers will be included in ICICSE 2024 Conference Proceedings, which will be archived in IEEE Xplore , and indexed by EI Compendex, Scopus, and other indexing services. ICICSE 2024 is listed in IEEE conference calendar: https://conferences.ieee.org/conferences\_events/conferences/conferencedetails/61805
